User Scenario: Sam is a junior in Computer Science and is concentrating in Software Engineering. As he is an international student, he needs a platform to look for summer full time or fall part time internship opportunities that match his skill set and where he can learn and grow as an individual.
User Story: As a computer science junior, I need to find an application that will help me to apply for Full Stack Developer internship roles so that I can gain experience in the job area that I am interested in.
Features: 
Filter option: to narrow down the search.
Direct message to employers/HR: to communicate directly with the HR.
Resume: to attach it with all of my applications.
